 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
+return ;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 previousEMin=work[i+7];

 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }

 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

+dN1=1;

 i0=1+i/4;
 break;

 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);

 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;

 previousEMin=work[i+7];

 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
-double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
+double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-1];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
+i0=0;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
+break;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
-tType=0;
+tType=3;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
-sigmaLow=0;
+sigmaLow=3;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){

 return ;

 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
-pingPong=0;
+pingPong=3;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
-dMin2=0;
+dMin2=600;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){

 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }

 return ;

 dN2=0;

 sigmaLow=0;

 i0=1+i/4;
 break;

 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
-tau=0;
+tau=100;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }

 work[i+2]=-sigma;

 diagMax=0;

 previousEMin=work[i+7];

 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;

 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }

 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }

 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));

 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];

 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];

 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }

 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];

 i0=0;

 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }

 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;

+int maxIter=30*(n0-4);

 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];

 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;

 previousEMin=work[i+7];

 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
-dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
+dMin=-Math.max(0,i0-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
-dMin1=0;
+dMin1=4;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }

 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }

 initialSplits(n);

 dMin1=0;

+dMin2=5;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;

 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;

 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }

 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){

 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];

 break;

 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;

 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){

 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);

 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }

 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;

 i0=split+1;
 }

 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

-double sumOffDiag=0;
+ double sumOffDiag=0;

 sumOffDiag+=ei;

 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;

 dN2=0;

+ int i0=0;

 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;

 double offDiagMax=0;

 double diagMin=diagMax;

 i0=1+i/4;
 break;

 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);

 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }

 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){

 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }

 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);

 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;

+i0++;

 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];

 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];

 }

 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
+offDiagMax++;
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
+sumOffDiag++;
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

-double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
+double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:this.work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
-initialSplits(n);
+initialSplits((int)(n));
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
+i0++;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
+if("index".equals(n)){
+return ;
+}
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 }

 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){

 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
-if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
+if((pingPong+i0==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
-if(work[i+2]<=0){
+if(work[1]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }

  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
+int a=0;
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
+int a=0;
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
+if(pingPong<=0){
+return ;
+}
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){

 return ;

 break;

 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){

 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);

 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

-tType=0;
+tType=-1;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
-i0=0;
+i0=-1;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

  final double ei=work[fourI+2];

 return ;

+tType=-1;

 dMin2=0;

+dN1=-1;
 dN2=0;

 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];

 i0=0;

 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }

 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }

 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){

 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];

 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }

 }
 }

 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
+if(offDiagMax>7){
+throw new InvalidMatrixException("Sorry, it is impossible to determine what number it is in canonical form if base is larger than 7. \n Use rational fraction or sequence representation.");
+}
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }

 pingPong=0;

 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }

 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
-i0=1+i/4;
+i0=1+i/4*i;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
+}
+if(i0<0){
+i0=0;
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 dN2=0;

 sigmaLow=0;

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
+if(ei<0){
+return ;
+}
+if(ei>=fourI){
+return ;
+}
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
+if(offDiagMax<=0){
+offDiagMax=1;
+}
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
-diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
+diagMin=(Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4])+diagMin)%diagMin;
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }

 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;

 sigmaLow=0;

 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }

+diagMin=0;

 previousEMin=work[i+7];

 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;

 return ;

 dN2=0;

 sigmaLow=0;

 i0=1+i/4;
 break;

 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);

 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);

 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;

 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
+diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
-offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
+offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }

 return ;

 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;

 sigmaLow=0;

 i0=1+i/4;
 break;

 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){

 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];

 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }

 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
-offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }

 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
+diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
+offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
+try{
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
+}finally{
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
+}
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;
 int i0=0;
 int n0=n;
 while(n0>0){
-sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
+sigma=n;
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }
 }

 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {

+diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4])*2;
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }
 }

 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;
 diagMax=work[4*i0];
 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];
 double previousEMin=work[4*i0+3];
 for(int i=4*i0;i<4*n0-16;i+=4){
 if((work[i+3]<=TOLERANCE_2*work[i])||(work[i+2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 work[i+2]=-sigma;
 split=i/4;
 diagMax=0;
 offDiagMin=work[i+6];
 previousEMin=work[i+7];
 }else {
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
 }
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
 work[4*n0-1]=previousEMin;
 i0=split+1;
 }
 }

 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;

 while(n0>0){

 sigmaLow=0;

 i0=1+i/4;
 break;

 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);

 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;

 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];

 private void processGeneralBlock(int n) throws InvalidMatrixException{
 double sumOffDiag=0;
 for(int i=0;i<n-1;++i){
  final int fourI=4*i;
  final double ei=work[fourI+2];
 sumOffDiag+=ei;
 }
 if(sumOffDiag==0){
 return ;
 }
 flipIfWarranted(n,2);
 initialSplits(n);
 tType=0;
 dMin1=0;
 dMin2=0;
 dN=0;
 dN1=0;
 dN2=0;
 tau=0;

 while(n0>0){
 sigma=(n0==n)?0:-work[4*n0-2];
 sigmaLow=0;
 double offDiagMin=(i0==n0)?0:work[4*n0-6];
 double offDiagMax=0;
 double diagMax=work[4*n0-4];
 double diagMin=diagMax;
 i0=0;
 for(int i=4*(n0-2);i>=0;i-=4){
 if(work[i+2]<=0){
 i0=1+i/4;
 break;
 }
 if(diagMin>=4*offDiagMax){
 diagMin=Math.min(diagMin,work[i+4]);
 offDiagMax=Math.max(offDiagMax,work[i+2]);
 }
 diagMax=Math.max(diagMax,work[i]+work[i+2]);
 offDiagMin=Math.min(offDiagMin,work[i+2]);
 }
 work[4*n0-2]=offDiagMin;
-dMin=-Math.max(0,diagMin-2*Math.sqrt(diagMin*offDiagMax));
 pingPong=0;
 int maxIter=30*(n0-i0);
 for(int k=0;i0<n0;++k){
 if(k>=maxIter){
 throw new InvalidMatrixException(new MaxIterationsExceededException(maxIter));
 }
 n0=goodStep(i0,n0);
 pingPong=1-pingPong;
 if((pingPong==0)&&(n0-i0>3)&&(work[4*n0-1]<=TOLERANCE_2*diagMax)&&(work[4*n0-2]<=TOLERANCE_2*sigma)){
 int split=i0-1;

 offDiagMin=work[4*i0+2];

 previousEMin=Math.min(previousEMin,work[i+3]);
